Bootstrap: localimage
From: /n/netscratch/kempner_dev/Lab/bdesinghu/Agent/alchemi/alchemi_ht/alchemi_ht.sif

%post
    # The base image (alchemi_ht.sif) already has:
    #   PyTorch, CUDA, ALCHEMI, AIMNet2, RDKit, pandas, ASE,
    #   scikit-learn, joblib, numpy (<2)
    #
    # Only install the packages that are genuinely missing.

    # HuggingFace Transformers for ChemBERTa / MoLFormer foundation models
    pip install transformers tokenizers

    # XGBoost (optional — RandomForest from sklearn works, but XGBoost
    # gives a stronger surrogate Brain when ground-truth data is plentiful)
    pip install xgboost

    # GNN encoder is implemented in pure PyTorch (SchNet-style),
    # so torch-geometric is NOT required.

%environment
    export LC_ALL=C
    export CUDA_CACHE_DISABLE=0
    export PYTHONNOUSERSITE=1
    export WARP_CACHE_PATH=/tmp/warp_cache

%help
    Container for ALCHEMI Phase 6: Latent-Space Active Learning.
    Extends alchemi_ht.sif with:
      - HuggingFace Transformers (ChemBERTa encoder)
      - XGBoost (optional surrogate Brain upgrade)
